data.text:
The popular small-screen couple Sanaya Irani and Mohit Sehgal tied knot on January 25 earlier this year.

The popular small-screen couple Sanaya Irani and Mohit Sehgal tied knot on January 25 earlier this year. The newlywed couple had a grand beach wedding, which made news for all the happy reasons. Sanaya and Mohit got married at the Plush beach resort, Planet Hollywood in South Goa. Sanaya and Mohit’s wedding pictures were out soon after their lavish wedding and the social media went gaga over it. But the complete wedding album with unseen photographs from the wedding posted on Instagram will make you love this gorgeous pair even more.

Sanaya Irani and Mohit Sehgal met on the sets of Miley Jab Hum Tum and since then they have been dating for last five years. The couple had a two day wedding affair which began from January 24. They had a sangeet night along with cocktail party on January 24 followed by the Haldi ritual on January 25th morning and they had a proper Punjabi wedding. The newlyweds are also called as MoNaya by their fans and isn’t this way too cute?

On January 24, there was a volleyball match fought between Sanaya and Mohit’s families. Further there was a cocktail party which will be located on the beach. The groom was seen wearing a sherwani whereas his bride was wearing a pink lehenga choli which was designed by the renowned fashion designer Roshni Chopra. In the reception, Mohit wore a tuxedo suit while Sanaya don a white wedding attire. Sanaya and Mohit’s grand beach wedding pictures are surely making us fall in love with them.

Television actors and duo’s best friends Drashti Dhami, Raqesh Vashisth, Ridhi Dogra, Barun Sobti, Arjun Bijlani and some more were present on their special day. Here we have the entire wedding album of Sanaya and Mohit, have a look at it:

Sanaya Irani and Mohit Sehgal joined the long list of popular Indian celebrities to tie the knot in the year 2016. Several high-profile weddings took place with the television industry. Couples like Divyanka Tripathi and Vivek Dahiya, Sambhavna Seth and Avinash Dwivedi, Siddhant Karnick and Megha Gupta, Hunar Hale and Mayank Gandhi had grand weddings in the year.

On the work front, Sanaya Irani’s last prominent role was in Rangrasiya, which aired on Colors TV. There are reports of Sanaya making her comback with Kuch Rang Pyar Ke Aise Bhi producer Yash Patnaik’s Beyond Dreams serial on Sony Entertainment. If the rumours are to be belived, Sanaya will be seen in a a different character, that of a mentally challenged girl in this yet to be titled serial. As for Sanaya Irani’s actor husband, Mohit Shaigal is concerend, the handsome star was previously seen in Sarojini – Ek Nayi Pehal. We wish this adorable pair to touch new heights on both personal and professional fronts. (Photo credits: Wedding Leaves Instagram)
